OPERATION CODE
  I/O Operations
    10 - read from keyboard into specific location in memory
    11 - write a word from specific location in memory to the screen
  Load/Store
    20 - Load a word from a specific location in memory into the accumulator
    21 - Store a word from the accumulator to a specific location in memory
  Arithmetic Operations
    30 - Add a word from specific location in memory into the accumulator and leave result in accumulator
    31 - Subtract ""
    32 - Divide
    33 - Multiply
  Control Operations
    40 - Branch to specific location in memory
    41 - Branch to specific location in memory if accumulator is negative
    42 - Branch to specific location in memory if accumulator is 0
    43 - Halt, program has completed its task
